{
  "texts": [
    "Incorporating a camera can be advantageous in texture-limited scenarios.",
    "Those with greater computational resources can explore advanced capabilities offered by deep learning-based LiDAR odometry.We anticipate the ongoing expansion of LiDAR odometry and believe that resolving the challenges through deep learning and multi-modal sensor fusion will pave the way for a general solution.",
    "Furthermore, we expect that the continuous development of both LiDAR sensors and odometry algorithms will lead to the emergence of even more accurate and robust odometry solutions in the future.Funding Open Access funding enabled and organized by Seoul National University.",
